load dataset

urlfile<-"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/darlyhounty/datasets/main/maple_dojoboss.csv"

Dojo_boss<-read.csv(url(urlfile),check.names = FALSE)

change type

Dojo_boss$HP <- gsub(",","",Dojo_boss$HP)
Dojo_boss$HP<-as.numeric(Dojo_boss$HP)

trelliscopejs

Dojo_boss %>%
  mutate(img=img_panel(img)) %>%
  trelliscope("Dojo_boss",nrow=2,ncol=5,path="rmarkdown_files")

plot Floor and blood graph

attach(Dojo_boss)
qplot(Floor,HP,data=Dojo_boss,color=PDR,main ="Maplestory Dojo Boss HP")+
  geom_line()
